data.description: Welcome to 106 Flycatcher Way.  This special home is located on the Lodge-side of the Lake in the sought after Trilogy at Lake Frederick 55+ Active Adult Resort Style Living Community by the Award-Winning Shea Builders. Designer Upgrades abound in this elegantly appointed NICE model: Elevated Premium Lot*Extended 3-Car Garage with EV Charger*Glass Stacking Doors at Dining Room and Great Room* *Spacious Covered Patio  offering Views of Nature*Additional Cabinetry & Counter Space in Laundry Room*Stainless Steel Kitchen Appliances*Granite Kitchen Island*Engineered Hardwood Floors on the Main Level*Tray Ceiling in Primary Bedroom with Ensuite and Walk-in Closet on the Main Level*Finished Walk-out Lower Level to a Trex Deck*Inground Irrigation System*Custom Window Treatments including Remote Control Blinds*Retractable Blade Ceiling Fans. On the Main Level you will also find a 2nd Bedroom with a 2nd Full Bathroom, an Office, Pantry, Dining Room and Great Room. The Lower Level features a large 3rd Bedroom with Walk-in Closet, 3rd Full Bathroom, Kitchenette, Recreation Area, Workshop Space, Storage Space and a Water Purification System.  Custom Landscaping, Hardscape, and Programable Lighting on the Front Covered Porch and Back Covered Patio add unique finishing touches to the exterior of the home.  Trilogy promotes Health and Wellness as well as the Preservation of Nature. In the community you will find Hiking and Biking paths, an Athletic Center, Indoor and Outdoor Pools, Tennis & Pickleball Courts, Picnic Area, Dog Park, and the cozy Shenandoah Lodge with Meeting Rooms for Member Clubs & Activities, Event Center, Cooking Room, Arts Room, Bar, Lounge Pool Tables, Golf Simulator, Games Room, Library, Coffee Bar, Gift Shop, Firepit, and the renowned Region's 117-  Farm to Table Restaurant. The Shenandoah HOA & Shenandoah Lodge are professionally managed.  Monthly HOA fee includes the Maintenance of Lawns, Common Areas and Neighborhood Roads, Trash Removal, Recycling and Daily Updates on Neighborhood Activities and Announcements. Trilogy is adjacent to Lake Frederick State Recreation Area with Fishing, Boat Dock, Boat Rentals, and 8-mile Nature Trail. Within 1 hour of Dulles Airport, and minutes from Routes 66, 81, 50 & 7, Churches, Schools, Universities, Hospitals, Doctors, Restaurants, Shopping, Local, State, National Parks and Recreation Areas. Come see all that Trilogy at Lake Frederick has to offer and make this beautiful house your new home!
